The 'Eclipse' was renowned for her swiftness . 
One day she passed along an old darkey on shore , absorbed in his own matters , did not notice what steamer it was . 
Presently someone asked 'Any boat gone up ? 'Yes , sah . 
'Was she going fast ? 'Oh , so so loafin' along . 
'Now , do you know what boat that was ? 'No , sah . 
'Why , uncle , that was the Eclipse . 
